Package: descriptiveStats
Title: Descriptive Statistics Functions for Numeric Vectors
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ryad", "Lachemi", , "ryadlachemi@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A package which implements multiple descriptive statistics functions. This includes the mean, median, mode, 1st quartile, 3rd quartile and the interquartile range. These are called used calc_YOURFUNCTION.
